Name: moa_optim
Title: Mixture-of-Agents Applied for Regression Performance Optimization
Experiment: Change the manual_weights only (i.e., [weight, bias]) and try to optimize the MSE as smaller as possible based on the performance in the previous runs. Experiment 1. Run as it is using the user_prompt provided on ml_regression data. Experiment 2. Augment the user_prompt using Chain-of-thought approach so that the MoA can better optimize weights for the regression task. Run Experiment 2 using that prompt. DO NOT attempt more than those two experiments to improve performance. Performance decline is fine, just report so. Please write a report after Experiment 1 and 2, comparing optimization performance (changes on mean squared errors across 30 iterations) to baseline.
